			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">The spell would be a damage mitigation spell.
<br />

<br />
Here is how it works, The mage casts this spell on themselves.
<br />

<br />
The effect cause melee damage on the pet to be mitigated by 50%.
<br />

<br />

<br />
The catch is it acts like invisibility, in that as soon as you cast another spell it disappears. In effect you are trading your own dps for pet tanking ability. 
<br />

<br />
The logic being that you are focusing all your energies into controling your pet and that casting would break that concentration.
<br />

<br />

<br />
Casting time 8 sec
<br />
ReCast 2.5 sec
<br />
Duration 2 min
<br />
mana cost 450
<br />
level 61</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
			</tr>
		</table></td>
	</tr>
