Here is another idea.
<br />

<br />

<br />
This spell would create a health pact with the pet.
<br />

<br />

<br />
Mage casts spell to bind with pet.
<br />

<br />

<br />
For every 10 points of damage the pet takes the mage loses 1 point of mana.
<br />

<br />
I dont know if the ratio would wourk at 10:1 but the concept remains the same.
<br />

<br />
The spell cost would be 400 and take 5 seconds to cast.
<br />

<br />
It only works on pets level 60 an higher. 
<br />

<br />
It only works for summoned pets.
<br />

<br />
This would still allow you to nuke but the more you nuke the less you can tank.
<br />

<br />

<br />
I dont know what a high end mage mana regen looks like ft 15 + mc 3+ armor + mod rod + horse. But the ratio should work out to be so that a mage could tank down a mob with minimal nuking at there gear level. and be at 10-20 % mana when done.
