				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I prefer my idea of the aaxp skills to have pets mitergate damage better, remember it would only help if you solo, and perhaps during enrage give you an extra second to get the pet off the mob. It is not over powering at all, and as we all know our pets need something to make them more viable in PoP zones and I am sure in the coming expansion as well. Many of us want a way to make the mage class more reliant on our pets, well this is a way that I am sure would be the number one item all mages would rush to get. I am sure were it to go live, we would all get it, and be damn glad. I know I would be.
<br />

<br />
Calebe</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
			</tr>
